title: The Immortal Emperor Luo Wuji Has Returned
description: Disciples and brothers betrayed one after another, and a generation of immortals fell. Though the body is dead, the soul is immortal! And with the most precious "Supreme Emperor's Scripture" to reverse the cause and effect, return to the earth, break the karmic barrier, and cast the divine personality again! This life will make the name of "Wuji" above the sun and moon!
author: Luoshu
